actions-list.actionItem: The House adjourned. The next meeting is scheduled for 12:00 p.m. on January 5, 2023.

actions-list.header: On motion to adjourn Agreed to by the Yeas and Nays: 216

actions-list.actionItem: Mr. Cole moved that the House do now adjourn.
The Clerk led the House in reciting the Pledge of Allegiance to the Flag.
The Clerk announced approval of the Journal.
Today's prayer was offered by the House Chaplain, Chaplain Margaret Grun Kibben.
The House convened, starting a new legislative day.
